data.description: Come check out this newly renovated home on just under five and a half acres! This 3 bed, 2 bath home has a spacious open floor plan, an office (not included in bedroom count), a huge shop with 220 and a loft for storage! Two more outbuildings are on the fully fenced property, with plenty of room for your animals, equipment, etc. This home has a new metal roof, a water softener system, and plenty of tasteful updates that you won't want to miss! *Listing agent related to sellers
